1
00:00:27,950 --> 00:00:30,890
♫ Ask the sword, the knife, to cast away resentment ♫

2
00:00:30,890 --> 00:00:34,600
♫  I fear that new and old grudges will add to my troubles ♫

3
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:37,600
♫ Ask each tactic, each trick, to test who is more skilled ♫

4
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:41,280
♫ The ups and downs of life are difficult to predict ♫

5
00:00:41,280 --> 00:00:44,580
♫ Ask the road and journey across remote lands  ♫

6
00:00:44,580 --> 00:00:47,930
♫ Where is my soul mate? I'm so lonely ♫

7
00:00:47,930 --> 00:00:50,820
♫ Ask the rain and clear skies about the troubles on my mind ♫

8
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:54,630
♫ Face the moon every day and night ♫

9
00:00:54,630 --> 00:00:57,570
♫ Ask the flowers and leaves, their colors are perfect ♫

10
00:00:57,570 --> 00:01:01,290
♫ Happiness and pain are fleeting; how many springs remain? ♫

11
00:01:01,290 --> 00:01:04,140
♫ Ask autumn and winter, the snowstorm continues ♫

12
00:01:04,140 --> 00:01:07,150
♫ The rainbow scatters easily but the days are hard to endure ♫

13
00:01:07,150 --> 00:01:10,370
♫ No one knows why the flowers blossomed early ♫

14
00:01:10,370 --> 00:01:13,760
♫ Heaven doesn't laugh, for it has grown old ♫

15
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:16,960
♫ The pugilist world is small, but the rest of the world is vast ♫

16
00:01:16,960 --> 00:01:20,280
♫ I've forgotten those who are gone ♫

17
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:23,760
♫ No one knows why the flowers withered early ♫

18
00:01:23,770 --> 00:01:27,120
♫ Heaven feels no sorrow, for it has grown old ♫

19
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:30,480
♫ The heroes have died and little time is left ♫

20
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:36,650
♫ I've forgotten those who are gone ♫

21
00:01:44,700 --> 00:01:49,950
[Word of Honor]

22
00:01:49,950 --> 00:01:52,900
[Episode 32]

23
00:01:52,900 --> 00:01:55,160
[Saijun Manor]

24
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:59,510
"In the past, we lived prosperous lives of fine wine and tail-feather headpieces. Now, the objects remain the same, yet the people have changed."

25
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:02,380
"Although the jade steps and engraved railings remain along the moon river,
(T/N: Based off of poem "Lady Yu" by Li Yu)

26
00:02:02,380 --> 00:02:03,740
the people standing by them

27
00:02:03,740 --> 00:02:05,720
are so different from me."

28
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:07,920
As the world changes, relationships change into indifference easily.

29
00:02:07,930 --> 00:02:11,290
Zishu, let's drink an entire glass as punishment!

30
00:02:11,290 --> 00:02:13,510
Well said! Come, Ping An, fill it up.

31
00:02:13,510 --> 00:02:15,240
Old Sick Ghoul, don't even think about it!

32
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,890
Before Master left, he ordered me

33
00:02:16,890 --> 00:02:19,580
to carefully watch over you.

34
00:02:21,250 --> 00:02:23,730
I'll only drink this one bowl. It's not a big deal, is it?

35
00:02:23,730 --> 00:02:25,660
It is.

36
00:02:25,660 --> 00:02:27,710
Not even a drop is allowed!

37
00:02:28,460 --> 00:02:30,990
Wu Xi, aren't you making it difficult for me?

38
00:02:30,990 --> 00:02:33,020
You know that I can't be happy without wine!

39
00:02:33,020 --> 00:02:36,560
Lord Zhou, you made it difficult for me first.

40
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:38,250
Your injury is tricky and odd,

41
00:02:38,250 --> 00:02:41,140
so even if your body could regulate it at its utmost condition,

42
00:02:41,140 --> 00:02:43,690
I can't guarantee that I can heal you.

43
00:02:43,690 --> 00:02:45,550
What more is there to say?

44
00:02:46,690 --> 00:02:49,410
Before you've healed, wine, sex, wealth, and anger

45
00:02:49,410 --> 00:02:51,200
will have nothing to do with you!

46
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:54,740
Wu Xi, when you're talking seriously,

47
00:02:54,740 --> 00:02:56,430
you're too cute.

48
00:02:56,430 --> 00:02:58,260
I don't need you to guarantee,

49
00:02:58,260 --> 00:03:02,020
fifty-percent is enough. As men, we should drink more.

50
00:03:03,130 --> 00:03:06,480
If you don't listen, I'll tattle to Master when he comes back.

51
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:08,420
Fine. I'll just not drink.

52
00:03:08,420 --> 00:03:09,980
I'll also tattle to him.

53
00:03:09,980 --> 00:03:12,380
A wicked girl was making things difficult for me.

54
00:03:13,070 --> 00:03:16,940
My Lord Zhou, your abilities to smell and taste were lost long ago,

55
00:03:16,940 --> 00:03:19,110
so what's the difference between whether you drink or not?

56
00:03:19,110 --> 00:03:20,310
Drink some tea.

57
00:03:20,310 --> 00:03:21,530
You! No...

58
00:03:21,530 --> 00:03:23,190
Let's drink.

59
00:03:23,190 --> 00:03:25,090
Here.

60
00:03:25,090 --> 00:03:27,260
- Drink!
- It's not the wine we're drinking.

61
00:03:27,260 --> 00:03:29,970
It's the feeling we're drinking.

62
00:03:30,980 --> 00:03:34,770
Zishu, it seems like we won't be able to drink together once again.

63
00:03:34,770 --> 00:03:39,330
I remembered that we once agreed that once we reunited, we'd drink until we got drunk.

64
00:03:39,330 --> 00:03:42,480
While I was waiting all of those years in Nanjiang, the wine got cold,

65
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:45,230
but the old friend seemed to have no intention of showing up.

66
00:03:45,230 --> 00:03:47,370
I also remember someone had once asked me

67
00:03:47,370 --> 00:03:50,510
to find him a slender Nanjiang lady.

68
00:03:50,510 --> 00:03:52,610
Turns out, I've found quite a few,

69
00:03:52,610 --> 00:03:54,800
but some people...

70
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:58,220
Here, let's have another drink.

71
00:03:58,220 --> 00:03:59,290
- Another cup!
- Okay!

72
00:03:59,290 --> 00:04:02,510
This time, you can't leave until you're drunk!

73
00:04:02,510 --> 00:04:03,570
A'Xiang.

74
00:04:03,570 --> 00:04:05,210
Lord Seventh.

75
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:10,330
A'Qin Lai, didn't I order you to stay with Chengling? Why are you back first?

76
00:04:10,330 --> 00:04:11,560
Where's Chengling?

77
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:14,480
Young Master Chengling is fine. However, he doesn't want me to assist him anymore.

78
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:16,040
What happened?

79
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:17,840
I don't know, either.

80
00:04:17,840 --> 00:04:20,120
Sect Leader Shen asked Young Master Chengling

81
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:23,810
if he knew that Sir Wen Kexing was Ghost Valley's chief.

82
00:04:23,810 --> 00:04:26,260
Young Master Chengling threw a tantrum and cried.

83
00:04:26,260 --> 00:04:29,150
Later, he asked me to come back.

84
00:04:29,150 --> 00:04:31,890
Chengling has discovered Old Wen's identity.

85
00:04:31,890 --> 00:04:35,960
Since it has come to this point, I need to find Old Wen and come up with a plan.

86
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:39,300
Lord Zhou, I pulled all the resources I could from Nanjiang

87
00:04:39,300 --> 00:04:41,910
to create this elixir of life for you.

88
00:04:41,910 --> 00:04:43,360
That won't be necessary.

89
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:46,370
I'm only going to resolve the misunderstanding between Old Wen and Chengling.

90
00:04:46,370 --> 00:04:49,480
Old Wen has promised me that he will no longer take notice of Ghost Valley's matters.

91
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:51,690
He'd only gone to the valley to obtain something important

92
00:04:51,690 --> 00:04:53,410
and then he would live a cloistered life with me.

93
00:04:53,410 --> 00:04:56,330
Just in case, please accept it.

94
00:04:56,330 --> 00:04:58,770
No matter how severe the injuries are, my medicine

95
00:04:58,770 --> 00:05:02,180
can guarantee to recover five days of a person's life.

96
00:05:04,250 --> 00:05:06,470
What if Sir Wen needs it?

97
00:05:06,470 --> 00:05:08,140
Don't jinx him, all right?

98
00:05:08,140 --> 00:05:09,720
Take it.

99
00:05:15,730 --> 00:05:18,880
[Tea Water]

100
00:05:20,350 --> 00:05:22,960
Sir, your dishes.

101
00:05:30,980 --> 00:05:33,500
“I'll temporarily set the white deer free among the green cliffs

102
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:36,810
and mount them when the need to visit you in the mountains arises". (T/N: Tianmu Mountain Ascended in a Dream by poet Li Bai)

103
00:05:36,810 --> 00:05:40,600
Rumors have made Ghost Valley seem dark and mysterious.

104
00:05:41,220 --> 00:05:45,880
Yet Mount Qingya seems to be a quiet place.

105
00:05:52,740 --> 00:05:55,490
Why are you still here? Hurry! If you don't hurry, you won't make it!

106
00:05:55,490 --> 00:05:58,890
- Brother, what's there to see?
- Haven't you heard?

107
00:05:58,890 --> 00:06:01,680
The Ghost Valley Chief has been surrounded and the Five Lakes Alliance has forced him onto White Deer Cliff!

108
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:03,960
He's about to be executed.

109
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:06,990
Once their chief dies, wouldn't the demons disappear?

110
00:06:06,990 --> 00:06:10,000
If you want to enjoy some entertainment, you better hurry. Otherwise, you won't be able to find a place to stand on White Deer Cliff!

111
00:06:10,010 --> 00:06:12,030
I'll be leaving first! I won't wait for you!

112
00:06:12,030 --> 00:06:14,370
- Let's go!
- Let's go.

113
00:06:57,570 --> 00:07:01,140
Brother Wen, stop messing around.

114
00:07:01,140 --> 00:07:03,610
Obediently surrender yourself.

115
00:07:03,610 --> 00:07:05,240
Listen to my word of advice!

116
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:08,750
I will leave your body whole!

117
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,880
What if I don't?

118
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:13,280
You savage brat!

119
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:16,940
No matter how highly skilled you are, can you defend against all of us?

120
00:07:16,940 --> 00:07:19,370
Everyone, don't try to talk sense into this monster!

121
00:07:19,370 --> 00:07:21,870
Let's all attack together and chop him to pieces!

122
00:07:21,870 --> 00:07:25,020
Kill him! Kill him!

123
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:28,840
I said! Whoever comes close dies!

124
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:31,690
I indeed have no method of killing you all.

125
00:07:31,690 --> 00:07:34,350
It depends on who wants to die first

126
00:07:34,350 --> 00:07:36,930
and who wants to live!

127
00:07:43,330 --> 00:07:46,800
Great warriors, look closely.

128
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:50,550
The World Armory Key that you all care so much about

129
00:07:50,550 --> 00:07:52,640
doesn't need any Glazed Armor.

130
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:56,660
As long as you have this key, you can open the door to the World's Armory directly.

131
00:07:56,660 --> 00:07:58,560
Do you want it?

132
00:08:00,580 --> 00:08:02,500
Kill me

133
00:08:02,500 --> 00:08:05,050
and the key is yours!

134
00:08:05,050 --> 00:08:07,030
Kill him! Kill him!

135
00:08:07,030 --> 00:08:09,550
Everyone, don't fall for his trap!

136
00:08:09,550 --> 00:08:13,670
Kill the monster first. Everyone will have a share of the World's Armory.

137
00:08:13,670 --> 00:08:17,520
I see, Venomous Scorpion. I, Wen Kexing, have had a life of twists and turns,

138
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:20,250
yet I'm falling to your despicable, evil schemes!

139
00:08:20,250 --> 00:08:23,190
Valley Chief Wen, all is fair in war.

140
00:08:23,190 --> 00:08:25,860
Are you the only one allowed to scheme against others?

141
00:08:25,860 --> 00:08:28,010
Are others not allowed to scheme against you?

142
00:08:28,010 --> 00:08:30,450
Why are you wasting words with him, Xie'er?

143
00:08:30,450 --> 00:08:34,740
Brother Wen, did you hear?

144
00:08:34,740 --> 00:08:38,360
It's not I, Zhao Jing, who wants to kill you!

145
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:41,590
- It's the world that wants to destroy you!
- I only hate that I was momentarily softhearted

146
00:08:41,590 --> 00:08:44,780
and didn't kill you to take revenge for my father!

147
00:08:44,780 --> 00:08:47,760
Zhen Ruyu lived a life of justice and honor!

148
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:50,460
Yet he was able to sire such an evil monster!

149
00:08:50,460 --> 00:08:52,560
If the Divine-Handed husband and wife can see this in the underworld,

150
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:54,970
they would be in great pain!

151
00:08:54,970 --> 00:08:58,510
Today, I will kill you to grant my brothers' wishes!

152
00:08:58,510 --> 00:09:01,530
I will also be cleansing Brother Zhen's bloodline!

153
00:09:01,530 --> 00:09:03,420
Chengling, I—

154
00:09:03,420 --> 00:09:06,730
Shut up! I will never forgive you for destroying my family!

155
00:09:06,730 --> 00:09:08,290
Chengling!

156
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:15,220
It's fine.

157
00:09:16,420 --> 00:09:17,880
I...

158
00:09:18,720 --> 00:09:21,150
I should not have harmed the Zhang family.

159
00:09:21,150 --> 00:09:23,770
Zhang Yusen did nothing wrong to my father.

160
00:09:24,470 --> 00:09:29,060
Chengling! Kill me to take revenge for your entire family!

161
00:09:29,970 --> 00:09:32,960
I am tired. Kill me.

162
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,560
I won't defend myself.

163
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:37,440
- Let go!
- Chengling, you can't go!

164
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:40,460
Stupid child, how can you believe the words of that devil?

165
00:09:40,460 --> 00:09:44,110
He won't be able to escape anyways. I can't let you go over there!

166
00:09:45,540 --> 00:09:47,100
I'm not lying!

167
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:49,560
Chengling! Come kill me!

168
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:50,820
I won't defend myself!

169
00:09:50,820 --> 00:09:53,150
You're lying! It's all a lie!

170
00:09:53,150 --> 00:09:56,760
Wen Kexing! You lied so heartlessly to Master!

171
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:59,010
I-I-

172
00:09:59,010 --> 00:10:01,010
He didn't lie to me!

173
00:10:16,180 --> 00:10:19,390
Chengling, do you trust me?

174
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:23,550
Zhou Zishu, don't try to trick Chengling.

175
00:10:23,550 --> 00:10:25,680
Brother Qin was so strong and righteous!

176
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:27,540
How could he have a traitorous disciple like you?

177
00:10:27,540 --> 00:10:30,800
Zhou Zishu! I admit that I lied to all of you!

178
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:32,410
Evil and righteousness do not go together!

179
00:10:32,410 --> 00:10:36,310
As Ghost Chief, I will definitely bring chaos to the martial arts world.

180
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:01,120
Save it.

181
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:18,590
Lord Zhou, you are from a famous sect!

182
00:11:18,590 --> 00:11:20,980
I am old friends with your master!

183
00:11:20,980 --> 00:11:24,310
If you return to the right side, it won't be too late!

184
00:11:24,310 --> 00:11:28,960
Today, Wen Kexing must be killed!

185
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:32,250
This bastard is skilled at scheming! He even tricked me!

186
00:11:32,250 --> 00:11:35,400
You can't fall for his tricks!

187
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:37,100
Stop with the pointless chatter!

188
00:11:37,100 --> 00:11:40,450
Are you coming one at a time? Or all at once?

189
00:11:40,450 --> 00:11:42,200
No sense of shame!

190
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:44,580
Failures of the martial arts world! A pair of devils!

191
00:11:44,580 --> 00:11:46,960
- Kill them!
- Kill them!

192
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:49,120
Bastard!

193
00:11:52,660 --> 00:11:55,430
Wen Kexing, I said before.

194
00:11:55,430 --> 00:11:59,420
If I ever saw you again, I would definitely kill you.

195
00:12:00,150 --> 00:12:04,900
Good! Let's see if you have that ability!

196
00:12:40,610 --> 00:12:42,140
Who's this white-cloaked person?

197
00:12:42,140 --> 00:12:47,090
This is the Sword Immortal Elder of Changming Mountain, Rong Xuan's Master.

198
00:12:47,090 --> 00:12:51,920
It is said he is the only one in the world who has mastered the Combined Six Cultivation Method.

199
00:12:51,920 --> 00:12:55,150
He is already one with the heavens and humanity.

200
00:12:55,150 --> 00:13:00,110
So mastering the Combined Six Cultivation Method brings such power.

201
00:13:26,540 --> 00:13:28,940
Elder Ye! Be careful!

202
00:13:33,420 --> 00:13:34,720
I'll help you!

203
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:36,200
Chengling!

204
00:13:45,420 --> 00:13:46,910
Chengling!

205
00:14:01,640 --> 00:14:04,190
Chengling! It's dangerous! Don't come over here!

206
00:14:04,190 --> 00:14:05,760
Move!

207
00:14:26,420 --> 00:14:28,000
Old Wen!

208
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:33,060
Old Wen!

209
00:14:41,010 --> 00:14:43,040
Why must it be like this?

210
00:14:45,350 --> 00:14:46,940
- Master!
- Chengling!

211
00:14:46,940 --> 00:14:48,840
Master!

212
00:14:53,380 --> 00:14:58,520
♫ The more you try to predict, the harder it is to predict ♫

213
00:14:58,520 --> 00:15:02,830
♫ Surrounded by old resentments ♫

214
00:15:03,740 --> 00:15:08,810
♫ The sky is full of rain, with love and hate so minuscule ♫

215
00:15:08,810 --> 00:15:13,130
♫ They bloom and float to and fro ♫

216
00:15:14,030 --> 00:15:18,920
♫ Struggling alone yet pretending all is smooth and peaceful ♫

217
00:15:18,920 --> 00:15:24,250
♫ Years pass again ♫

218
00:15:24,250 --> 00:15:29,390
♫ No way to hold on, no way to escape ♫

219
00:15:29,390 --> 00:15:33,860
♫ I'm insistent, but I let it pass ♫

220
00:15:33,860 --> 00:15:38,650
♫ Who is smiling? ♫

221
00:15:38,650 --> 00:15:42,390
Second Brother! Finding the Armory Key is more important.

222
00:15:46,580 --> 00:15:50,870
The Armory's Key is on Wen Kexing's body!

223
00:15:54,440 --> 00:15:59,500
♫ Who is offering a hug? ♫

224
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:04,800
♫ Who is has missed it again? ♫

225
00:16:04,800 --> 00:16:13,580
♫ Dreams are vague ♫

226
00:16:38,700 --> 00:16:40,700
Lord, you are awake?

227
00:16:40,700 --> 00:16:42,050
Where is this?

228
00:16:42,050 --> 00:16:44,300
This is Peace Hotel.

229
00:16:45,530 --> 00:16:48,080
Peace Hotel...

230
00:16:48,080 --> 00:16:49,720
It was a dream.

231
00:16:50,370 --> 00:16:51,620
Turns out it was just a dream.

232
00:16:51,620 --> 00:16:53,660
My Lord, do you need anything?

233
00:16:53,660 --> 00:16:56,590
The Lord who sent you here is a VIP of our Peace Hotel.

234
00:16:56,590 --> 00:16:59,350
He told us everything is on him.

235
00:17:00,210 --> 00:17:03,110
The Ghost Valley has pressured and dominated us for so long.

236
00:17:03,110 --> 00:17:05,090
Today, we're finally proud!

237
00:17:05,090 --> 00:17:07,190
Happy! Happy!

238
00:17:07,190 --> 00:17:09,530
We let that devil die so easily?

239
00:17:09,530 --> 00:17:10,950
That's too easy on him!

240
00:17:10,950 --> 00:17:14,900
That evil thief actually died whole! It's not fair!

241
00:17:14,900 --> 00:17:16,990
- Wouldn't you say so?
- That's right!

242
00:17:16,990 --> 00:17:20,740
Alliance Leader Zhao should've paraded his body throughout the streets!

243
00:17:20,740 --> 00:17:22,240
- Right!
- Right!

244
00:17:22,240 --> 00:17:24,060
Let's drink! Drink!

245
00:17:24,060 --> 00:17:28,450
Please forgive us. In this past half month, many martial arts world members have been here.

246
00:17:28,450 --> 00:17:31,360
There must have been some huge event today. It's been noisy the whole night.

247
00:17:31,360 --> 00:17:33,310
It is a little noisy indeed.

248
00:17:33,310 --> 00:17:35,750
Lord! Lord!

249
00:17:36,380 --> 00:17:39,520
My Lord! Are you all right?

250
00:17:39,520 --> 00:17:41,080
My Lord?

