278
00:19:26,310 --> 00:19:28,000
Scorpion,

279
00:19:31,250 --> 00:19:33,130
come here.

280
00:19:39,150 --> 00:19:41,330
Sit down.

281
00:19:42,030 --> 00:19:44,440
Didn't you just want to sit by me?

282
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:46,740
