290
00:20:23,980 --> 00:20:26,530
Enough! Today,

291
00:20:26,530 --> 00:20:28,320
I will take advantage of this opportunity

292
00:20:28,320 --> 00:20:31,580
and grandly introduce

293
00:20:31,580 --> 00:20:34,900
the young talent beside me

