00:20:34,900 --> 00:20:38,160
as my most beloved, good son!

295
00:20:40,230 --> 00:20:42,370
Zhao Xie'er!

296
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:47,990
To Sir Zhao! To Sir Zhao!

297
00:20:47,990 --> 00:20:50,820
To Sir Zhao!

