00:25:39,800 --> 00:25:41,300
A'Xiang!

355
00:25:43,800 --> 00:25:45,600
Brother Zhou.

356
00:25:45,600 --> 00:25:48,400
Lord Seventh and Great Shaman didn't come with you two?

