00:28:27,390 --> 00:28:30,220
I always knew what you wanted.

383
00:28:32,200 --> 00:28:34,600
I just never spoke of it.

384
00:28:35,460 --> 00:28:38,200
I thought I could change you slowly.

385
00:28:39,400 --> 00:28:41,300
Who would've thought

386
00:28:42,570 --> 00:28:45,310
I would be the one who changed in the end?

387
00:28:46,030 --> 00:28:47,820
I know!

388
00:28:50,000 --> 00:28:53,000
You wanted this foul, tumultuous world

389
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:56,100
