394
00:29:09,800 --> 00:29:12,400
To accompany your parents' deaths.

395
00:29:16,900 --> 00:29:18,600
In the past,

396
00:29:19,530 --> 00:29:22,270
I thought you were too extreme.

397
00:29:23,000 --> 00:29:25,900
You were blinded by your hatred.

398
00:29:42,510 --> 00:29:45,300
If you don't experience it yourself,

399
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:47,500
you don't know how much it hurts.

400
00:29:47,500 --> 00:29:51,400
♫  along the river  ♫

401
00:29:53,400 --> 00:29:57,800
The trap is set, yet where is the hunter?

402
00:29:59,100 --> 00:30:06,500
You've schemed for so long.

403
00:30:06,500 --> 00:30:12,800
Don't you want to see the ending?

404
00:30:12,800 --> 00:30:16,800
Your injury is serious in that once the nails are removed,

405
00:30:16,800 --> 00:30:21,600
