00:30:50,680 --> 00:30:55,300
Tomorrow is the day we reinitiate the Heroes Conference.

413
00:30:56,570 --> 00:30:59,260
My, Zhao Jing's, first cup of wine

414
00:30:59,260 --> 00:31:01,880
is to toast our lost brothers.

415
00:31:01,880 --> 00:31:05,360
I hope their spirits can protect our Five Lakes Alliance

416
00:31:05,360 --> 00:31:07,800
in choosing a righteous and honorable leader

417
00:31:07,800 --> 00:31:09,900
to lead us in destroying Ghost Valley

418
00:31:09,900 --> 00:31:12,900
and in wiping out this cancerous existence in the martial arts world.

419
00:31:12,900 --> 00:31:16,980
Here! Toast to our lost brothers!

420
00:31:18,790 --> 00:31:20,380
Toast.

421
00:31:22,330 --> 00:31:24,060
My second cup of wine

422
00:31:24,060 --> 00:31:27,230
is to toast everyone here.

423
00:31:27,230 --> 00:31:29,350
A toast to your bravery.

424
00:31:29,350 --> 00:31:33,160
Now, heroes of all paths have gathered at White Deer Village.

425
00:31:33,160 --> 00:31:35,810
Whether my Five Lakes Alliance can cleanse its past shame

426
00:31:35,810 --> 00:31:39,490
and achieve glory will all depend on this crucial battle.

427
00:31:39,490 --> 00:31:41,600
However, Ghost Valley has lurked for many years.

428
00:31:41,600 --> 00:31:44,180
They hold a geographical advantage and are hard to attack.

429
00:31:44,180 --> 00:31:46,500
This battle will most definitely be hard.

430
00:31:46,500 --> 00:31:49,200
