448
00:32:41,840 --> 00:32:43,500
Second Brother,

449
00:32:44,700 --> 00:32:47,720
this third cup of wine, I toast you.

450
00:32:47,720 --> 00:32:50,290
I hope your wish is granted tomorrow.

451
00:32:50,290 --> 00:32:52,000
Help Eldest Brother...

452
00:32:52,830 --> 00:32:55,140
