00:33:04,330 --> 00:33:07,110
Uncle Gao, and Uncle Lu's spirits

456
00:33:07,110 --> 00:33:08,960
can aid me as I successfully take my revenge!

457
00:33:08,960 --> 00:33:13,470
Brothers! Let us all toast Alliance Leader Zhao together!

458
00:33:14,480 --> 00:33:19,910
I hope Father takes the position of Supreme Leader of the martial arts world tomorrow.

459
00:33:20,490 --> 00:33:22,680
Scorpion, don't only look at what's in front of you.

460
00:33:22,680 --> 00:33:25,680
This battle is to uphold justice

461
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:29,730
and to wipe out devils! As for whether I become the Supreme Leader,

462
00:33:29,730 --> 00:33:32,500
