470
00:33:56,880 --> 00:34:00,450
Everyone! With Alliance Leader Zhao's leadership,

471
00:34:00,450 --> 00:34:02,920
who cares if they are 3,000 devils?

472
00:34:02,920 --> 00:34:05,710
