However, it just so happened that this young man's child

509
00:37:16,510 --> 00:37:19,330
ended up becoming the Chief of Ghost Valley.

510
00:37:30,080 --> 00:37:32,400
Fate toys with people, indeed.

511
00:37:34,290 --> 00:37:39,900
Changqing, if the one alive was you and not me,

512
00:37:41,180 --> 00:37:43,100
what would you do?

513
00:37:58,330 --> 00:38:00,390
Lord Duan, please.

514
00:38:06,390 --> 00:38:08,210
Officer Duan,

515
00:38:09,700 --> 00:38:13,200
have things changed?

516
00:38:16,280 --> 00:38:21,100
Alliance Leader Zhao, I have certainly misread you.

517
00:38:21,100 --> 00:38:25,360
Who would've thought you sided with both righteous and evil sides?

518
00:38:25,360 --> 00:38:29,980
Aside from being the Leader of Five Lakes Alliance, you are also the Leader of Venomous Scorpions.

519
00:38:29,980 --> 00:38:33,690
I lacked respect. I lacked respect, indeed.

520
00:38:33,690 --> 00:38:36,130
Officier Duan, it is my fault.

521
00:38:36,130 --> 00:38:38,900
However, it is a long story, and the timing was not right.

522
00:38:38,900 --> 00:38:41,430
It would be inconvenient for the world to know.

523
00:38:41,430 --> 00:38:44,300
However, if you must know,

524
00:38:44,300 --> 00:38:47,560
I would definitely not lie to my allies.

525
00:38:47,560 --> 00:38:49,380
Allies?

526
00:38:49,870 --> 00:38:53,690
How could the Window of Heaven dare to ally with the great Venomous Scorpions?

527
00:38:53,690 --> 00:38:56,300
You possess multiple identities.

528
00:38:56,300 --> 00:39:00,070
This was not something I originally should've interfered with,

529
00:39:00,070 --> 00:39:05,580
but Venomous Scorpions is a harmful existence that steals and kills everywhere.

530
00:39:05,580 --> 00:39:10,640
Buying humans and transforming them into Drug Men is something the world cannot accept!

531
00:39:11,810 --> 00:39:15,400
If the Window of Heaven were to openly support someone like you,

532
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:17,390
helping you become Supreme Leader and wipe out Ghost Valley,

533
00:39:17,390 --> 00:39:19,140
then if this were to get exposed in the future,

534
00:39:19,140 --> 00:39:23,150
the prince would take my head first!

535
00:39:23,150 --> 00:39:24,820
Officer Duan!

536
00:39:26,540 --> 00:39:30,060
I came today to inform you that

537
00:39:30,060 --> 00:39:33,350
after today, we are enemies, not friends.

538
00:39:33,350 --> 00:39:35,770
Next time we meet,

539
00:39:35,770 --> 00:39:39,250
don't blame me for not showing any mercy.

540
00:39:39,250 --> 00:39:42,310
- I will take my leave.
- Officer Duan! Please wait!

541
00:39:42,310 --> 00:39:44,340
There must be a misunderstanding.

542
00:39:44,340 --> 00:39:47,150
I, Zhao Jing, am not the Leader of Venomous Scorpions.

543
00:39:47,150 --> 00:39:49,950
The leader is the Scorpion King.

544
00:39:50,920 --> 00:39:54,250
He... counts as my ally as well.

545
00:39:54,250 --> 00:39:56,110
Ally?

546
00:39:56,900 --> 00:39:59,960
Is he not your adopted son?

547
00:39:59,960 --> 00:40:02,470
Yes, that's right.

548
00:40:02,470 --> 00:40:06,290
However, I did not know he performed so many evil acts behind my back.

549
00:40:07,400 --> 00:40:11,210
Officer Duan, can you specify

550
00:40:11,210 --> 00:40:13,940
what exactly Drug Men are?

551
00:40:19,080 --> 00:40:20,840
How was it?

552
00:40:22,360 --> 00:40:25,510
The human heart cannot bear testing.

553
00:40:29,520 --> 00:40:33,580
Zhao Jing said he would reinitiate the Heroes Conference

554
00:40:33,580 --> 00:40:36,060
and fight against the Ghost Valley to the end.

555
00:40:37,420 --> 00:40:41,620
Using evil to kill evil is not against the will of the heavens.

556
00:40:43,390 --> 00:40:45,790
After the battle,

557
00:40:45,790 --> 00:40:50,540
he will kill you and take over the Venomous Scorpions.

